&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://nx.dev/docs/features/enforce-module-boundaries" rel="noopener noreferrer"&gt;https://nx.dev/docs/features/enforce-module-boundaries&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

